*

00:40.108 --> 00:42.338
- * SHUT THE DOOR,
YOU WANNA LOOK TOUGH *

00:42.376 --> 00:44.846
* SHUT THE DOOR,
WANNA PLAY HARD *

00:44.878 --> 00:47.248
- DID YOU SEE THAT?

00:47.281 --> 00:49.381
- KIND OF HARD TO MISS.
- SO GROSS.

00:49.417 --> 00:52.087
- I THINK IT'S COOL.

00:52.120 --> 00:54.560
- I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU'RE
ACTUALLY DOING THIS...FOR HIM.

00:54.588 --> 00:55.758
- IT'S NOT FOR HIM.
- I MEAN,

00:55.789 --> 00:57.429
JUST BECAUSE HE'S YOUR BOYFRIEND
DOESN'T MEAN YOU HAVE TO--

00:57.458 --> 01:01.298
- HE'S NOT MY BOYFRIEND.
I DON'T DO BOYFRIENDS.

01:01.329 --> 01:03.129
BESIDES, HALF THE KIDS
IN SCHOOL

01:03.164 --> 01:04.504
HAVE THEIR NOSES
OR THEIR EARS PIERCED.

01:04.532 --> 01:06.572
ERICA JACOBSON EVEN HAS
HER BELLY BUTTON PIERCED.

01:06.600 --> 01:10.300
- ERICA JACOBSON IS A WHORE.
A-AND IT'S DANGEROUS.

01:10.338 --> 01:12.438
THIS GIRL IN TEXAS,
HER BOYFRIEND WENT TO KISS HER,

01:12.473 --> 01:14.313
HIS BRACES GOT CAUGHT
IN HER TONGUE RING,

01:14.342 --> 01:15.482
RIPPED IT CLEAR
OUT OF HER MOUTH.

01:15.509 --> 01:16.679
- THINGS LIKE THAT
ALWAYS HAPPEN IN TEXAS.

01:16.710 --> 01:19.180
- WHAT ABOUT THAT GUY WITH
THE STUD IN HIS NOSTRIL, HMM?

01:19.213 --> 01:21.183
GANGRENE SET IN. HE HAD TO HAVE
HIS ENTIRE NOSE AMPUTATED.

01:21.215 --> 01:22.315
- URBAN LEGEND.

01:22.350 --> 01:24.850
- WHO'S NEXT?

01:24.885 --> 01:28.785
TAKE OFF YOUR SHIRT, HONEY.

01:28.822 --> 01:30.722
SO WHICH ONE DO YOU WANT,
RIGHT OR LEFT?

01:30.758 --> 01:32.458
- I DON'T KNOW.

01:32.493 --> 01:36.733
- YOU KNOW,
MOST GUYS LIKE RIGHT.

01:36.764 --> 01:38.304
OKAY.

01:38.332 --> 01:41.702
- * HEY HEY HEY
HEY HEY HEY *

01:41.735 --> 01:43.595
* HEY HEY

01:43.637 --> 01:47.707
- EXCUSE ME,
IS--IS THIS GOING TO HURT?

01:47.741 --> 01:49.881
- OF COURSE.

01:49.910 --> 01:53.750
ARE YOU READY?
- MM-HMM.

01:53.781 --> 01:56.381
- * HEY HEY HEY HEY

01:56.417 --> 01:59.347
* HEY HEY HEY HEY HEY

01:59.387 --> 02:00.687
- OW!

02:00.721 --> 02:04.331
- * HEY HEY HEY HEY HEY

02:04.358 --> 02:08.728
*

02:08.762 --> 02:11.532
[dance music]

02:11.565 --> 02:18.435
*

02:18.472 --> 02:20.512
- NOTICE THAT PRACTICALLY EVERY
GUY IN HERE'S BEEN CRUISING US?

02:20.541 --> 02:22.841
- I SHOULD'VE WARNED YOU.
THE...CLIENTELE

02:22.876 --> 02:25.446
DOESN'T EXACTLY COME HERE
FOR THE FIVE-STAR CUISINE.

02:25.479 --> 02:27.519
EVERYBODY'S ALWAYS WISHING
THEY HAD A BOYFRIEND.

02:27.548 --> 02:29.818
WE ALL PICTURE HOW HE'D LOOK,
HOW HE'D SOUND,

02:29.850 --> 02:31.950
HOW NICE IT'D BE TO HAVE
SOMEONE TO SHARE YOUR LIFE,

02:31.985 --> 02:33.815
YOUR DREAMS,
YOUR DENTAL FLOSS.

02:33.854 --> 02:35.794
- A LITTLE DISCONCERTING
WHEN YOU'RE TRYING TO EAT.

02:35.823 --> 02:37.293
- SO HOW COME
SO FEW OF US HAVE ONE?

02:37.325 --> 02:38.525
THAT'S BECAUSE WE'RE LYING.

02:38.559 --> 02:39.959
MOST OF US COULDN'T COMMIT
TO A HOUSEPLANT.

02:39.993 --> 02:42.263
HOW ARE WE SUPPOSED TO COMMIT
TO HAVING A BOYFRIEND?

02:42.296 --> 02:45.196
YOU SHOULD SEE WHAT IT'S LIKE
WHEN BRIAN COMES HERE.

02:47.435 --> 02:49.535
I'M SO SORRY, I PROMISED
I WOULD NOT MENTION HIS NAME

02:49.570 --> 02:53.240
FOR TEN MINUTES.
- I'D SETTLE FOR FIVE.

02:53.274 --> 02:55.644
AND YOU'VE GOT TO STOP SMILING
LIKE THAT.

02:55.676 --> 02:57.306
- LIKE WHAT?
- LIKE THAT.

02:57.345 --> 02:58.675
IT MAKES ME WANT
TO COME ACROSS THE TABLE

02:58.712 --> 03:00.752
AND EAT YOU
LIKE A DESSERT.

03:00.781 --> 03:03.821
WOULD YOU LIKE SOME
WHIPPED CREAM WITH THAT, SIR?

03:03.851 --> 03:05.491
- I'D STAY AWAY
FROM THAT ONION, HONEY,

03:05.519 --> 03:06.689
ESPECIALLY IF YOU TWO
ARE PLANNING ON GOING

03:06.720 --> 03:07.690
AT IT ALL NIGHT.

03:07.721 --> 03:08.961
- MA, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

03:08.989 --> 03:09.959
- TRYING TO PAY MY BILLS.

03:09.990 --> 03:12.930
YOU GOT A PROBLEM
WITH THAT?

03:12.960 --> 03:16.330
- THIS IS--THIS IS YOUR, UH...
- MOTHER.

03:16.364 --> 03:17.904
- I'M DEBBIE, AND YOU'RE...

03:17.931 --> 03:20.731
GODDAMN GORGEOUS
IS WHAT YOU ARE.

03:20.768 --> 03:21.638
- MA, THIS IS DAVID.
AND I--

03:21.669 --> 03:23.969
I THOUGHT TONIGHT
WAS YOUR NIGHT OFF.

03:24.004 --> 03:25.474
- OH, YEAH, LORRAINE GOT
FOOD POISONING.

03:25.506 --> 03:27.976
I THINK IT WAS THE SHISH KABOB.
[laughs]

03:28.008 --> 03:30.238
I'M JUST KIDDING.

03:30.278 --> 03:32.778
OKAY, GOT TO GET CRANKING.

03:32.813 --> 03:34.783
GOT A LOT OF HUNGRY BOYS
TO FEED.

03:34.815 --> 03:38.415
JESUS, MY BACK
IS KILLING ME.

03:38.452 --> 03:39.992
- HEY.

03:40.020 --> 03:42.620
IF YOU LIFT FROM YOUR KNEES,

03:42.656 --> 03:44.326
TAKES THE PRESSURE OFF
YOUR BACK.

03:44.358 --> 03:47.658
YOU FEEL THAT?
- YEAH, I'LL REMEMBER THAT.

03:47.695 --> 03:51.625
YOU'RE AN ANGEL.
- NO, I'M A CHIROPRACTOR.

03:51.665 --> 03:52.665
- YOU'RE A DOCTOR?

03:52.700 --> 03:55.900
- YEAH.
- YOU'RE DATING A DOCTOR?

03:55.936 --> 03:58.466
HOW LONG WERE YOU PLANNING
ON HIDING HIM FROM ME?

03:58.506 --> 03:59.866
- AS LONG AS I COULD.

03:59.907 --> 04:02.337
- YOU'RE COMING FOR DINNER
TOMORROW NIGHT.

04:02.376 --> 04:03.336
- HE CAN'T.
- I CAN'T?

04:03.377 --> 04:05.647
- YOU GOT PLANS.
HE'S GOT PLANS. HE'S VERY BUSY.

04:05.679 --> 04:07.349
- DEBBIE, I'D LOVE TO.
- GOOD FOR YOU.

04:07.381 --> 04:09.551
I'LL SEE YOU THERE, 7:30.
- OKAY.

04:09.583 --> 04:11.893
[chuckles]

04:11.919 --> 04:15.689
- CRAIG?

04:15.723 --> 04:18.762
AREN'T YOU GOING TO SAY
ANYTHING?

04:21.362 --> 04:22.762
- JUSTIN'S NOT GAY.

04:22.796 --> 04:25.526
THOSE NUDE DRAWINGS YOU FOUND,

04:25.566 --> 04:27.636
THEY'RE PROBABLY JUST
AN ASSIGNMENT FOR ART CLASS.

04:27.668 --> 04:29.798
AND THE UNDERWEAR, I'M SURE
HE JUST BOUGHT IT FOR HIMSELF.

04:29.837 --> 04:31.537
- IT'S NOT HIS SIZE.

04:31.572 --> 04:34.782
- STILL, THAT'S NO REASON
TO SUSPECT THAT HE'S...

04:34.808 --> 04:36.878
- HE TOLD ME HIMSELF.
- SO WHAT?

04:36.910 --> 04:40.780
THAT DOESN'T MEAN ANYTHING.
A LOT OF KIDS THINK THAT.

04:40.814 --> 04:42.854
THEY'RE CONFUSED,
THEY'RE SCARED.

04:42.883 --> 04:44.853
- HE'S NOT CONFUSED.
HE'S NOT SCARED.

04:44.885 --> 04:47.415
HE KNOWS.

04:47.455 --> 04:48.655
THE SAME WAY
WE'VE ALWAYS KNOWN.

04:48.689 --> 04:51.019
- NO, NO, I HAVE NOT
ALWAYS KNOWN.

04:51.058 --> 04:54.058
- AT LEAST SUSPECTED.
- NO, YOU'VE SUSPECTED.

04:54.094 --> 04:55.934
HE'S NOT GAY.
HE'S...

04:55.963 --> 04:57.803
- WHAT, SENSITIVE?

04:57.831 --> 04:59.731
DIFFERENT?
ARTISTIC?

04:59.767 --> 05:01.067
- HE'S HIS OWN PERSON.

05:01.101 --> 05:02.801
YOU KNOW, NOT EVERY KID
IS THE QUARTERBACK

05:02.836 --> 05:03.936
ON THE FOOTBALL TEAM.

05:03.971 --> 05:05.711
- I THINK YOU BETTER TALK
TO HIM.

05:05.739 --> 05:08.509
- [chuckles]
AND SAY WHAT?

05:08.542 --> 05:10.442
"YOUR MOTHER THINKS
YOU'RE A HOMOSEXUAL"?

05:10.478 --> 05:12.048
- BEFORE HE GETS HIMSELF
INTO TROUBLE.

05:12.079 --> 05:14.979
BEFORE HE EXPOSES HIMSELF
TO GOD KNOWS WHAT.

05:15.015 --> 05:16.515
IF HE HASN'T ALREADY.

05:16.550 --> 05:19.790
- WAIT.

05:19.820 --> 05:21.420
YOU'RE SAYING
HE'S DOING THINGS?

05:21.455 --> 05:24.855
- HE'S...17.

05:24.892 --> 05:26.562
HOW NAIVE CAN YOU BE?

05:26.594 --> 05:27.804
- SO WHY DIDN'T YOU
TELL ME?

05:27.828 --> 05:30.458
- I PROMISED HIM
I WOULDN'T.

05:30.498 --> 05:33.498
- OH, THAT'S TERRIFIC.

05:33.534 --> 05:36.944
DON'T I HAVE A RIGHT TO KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON AROUND HERE?

05:36.970 --> 05:40.110
HEY, JUSTIN!
- HE'S NOT HERE.

05:40.140 --> 05:42.880
HE SAYS HE'S GOING TO DAPHNE'S,
BUT I KNOW HE'S NOT.

05:42.910 --> 05:46.050
- SO WHERE IS HE?

05:46.079 --> 05:49.419
- THE OTHER NIGHT, I FOUND HIM
IN A GAY BAR.

05:49.450 --> 05:50.850
- I DON'T FUCKING BELIEVE THIS,
JEN.

05:50.884 --> 05:54.664
YOU LET HIM GO TO THESE PLACES?
- I HAD NO IDEA.

05:54.688 --> 05:58.558
- WELL, I'M PUTTING A STOP
TO THIS RIGHT NOW.

05:58.592 --> 06:00.932
- THERE'S MORE.

06:00.961 --> 06:04.001
HE'S SEEING SOMEONE.

06:04.031 --> 06:07.741
- SO WHO IS THIS KID?
I'LL CALL HIS PARENTS.

06:07.768 --> 06:11.068
- HE'S NOT A KID.
HE'S A MAN.

06:11.104 --> 06:14.614
HIS NAME IS BRIAN KINNEY.

06:17.645 --> 06:19.445
- I SAY, IF IT WALKS
LIKE A BOYFRIEND...

06:19.480 --> 06:20.610
- TALKS LIKE
A BOYFRIEND...

06:20.648 --> 06:23.048
both: THEN IT MUST BE
A BOYFRIEND.

06:23.083 --> 06:24.893
- WOULD YOU TWO PLEASE
SHUT THE FUCK UP?

06:24.918 --> 06:26.888
- I THINK IT'S GREAT
THAT MIKEY'S GOT A STEADY.

06:26.920 --> 06:29.860
- HE'S NOT A STEADY.
WE WENT OUT TWICE.

06:29.890 --> 06:32.160
- AROUND HERE, THAT'S
A LONG-TERM RELATIONSHIP.

06:32.192 --> 06:33.992
NEXT THING YOU KNOW,
YOU'LL BE EXCHANGING RINGS.

06:34.027 --> 06:36.657
- MM, AND THEN THERE'LL BE ONE
OF THOSE COMMITMENT CEREMONIES

06:36.697 --> 06:38.197
WHERE, LIKE,
ALL 200 OF THE GUESTS

06:38.231 --> 06:41.101
HAVE SLEPT WITH ONE, IF NOT
BOTH, OF THE HAPPY COUPLE.

06:41.134 --> 06:42.644
- JUST, UM, PROMISE ME

06:42.670 --> 06:44.040
YOU WON'T WEAR
MATCHING WHITE SUITS.

06:44.071 --> 06:46.841
- THERE'S NO WAY THAT IS
EVER GOING TO HAPPEN.

06:46.874 --> 06:50.644
- WELL, THEN I SUGGEST YOU
WATCH OUT FOR THE WARNING SIGNS.

06:50.678 --> 06:51.808
- WHAT WARNING SIGNS?

06:51.845 --> 06:53.575
- LIKE WHEN
HE BRINGS YOU FLOWERS.

06:53.614 --> 06:56.654
- OR INVITES YOU AWAY FOR A
ROMANTIC WEEKEND IN THE COUNTRY.

06:56.684 --> 07:00.524
- NOT THAT YOU'LL SEE MUCH
BESIDE THE BEDROOM CEILING.

07:00.554 --> 07:02.064
- YOUR SHOT, MIKEY.

07:02.089 --> 07:05.159
- OH, OR THE MOST TELLTALE SIGN
OF ALL,

07:05.192 --> 07:06.862
WHEN HE MEETS
YOUR MOTHER,

07:06.894 --> 07:10.104
AND SHE INVITES HIM OVER
FOR DINNER.

07:11.999 --> 07:13.729
- SOMETHING THE MATTER?

07:13.767 --> 07:14.967
- I LOST MY GRIP.

07:15.002 --> 07:16.902
- GUESS WHAT I GOT TODAY.

07:16.937 --> 07:19.067
- A NEW BELL
FOR YOUR BICYCLE?

07:19.106 --> 07:22.106
- A NIPPLE RING.

07:22.142 --> 07:23.912
- EVERY PIECE OF TRASH
HAS SOMETHING

07:23.944 --> 07:25.554
STUCK THROUGH THEIR EAR
OR THEIR NOSE

07:25.579 --> 07:28.119
OR THEIR BELLY BUTTON
OR THEIR COCK.

07:28.148 --> 07:30.578
WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
I'M EVEN REMOTELY INTERESTED

07:30.618 --> 07:32.588
THAT YOU HAVE A RING
THROUGH YOUR TIT?

07:32.620 --> 07:35.560
- IT'S LATE.
I GOT WORK.

07:35.589 --> 07:37.189
- DON'T FORGET
ABOUT THIS FRIDAY.

07:37.224 --> 07:39.964
- WHAT'S THIS FRIDAY?
- YOU'RE TOO YOUNG TO KNOW.

07:39.993 --> 07:41.563
- TELL ME.

07:41.595 --> 07:44.665
- JUST SOME HEATHEN RITUAL
CALLED "STUDS IN SUDS."

07:44.698 --> 07:47.668
- STUDS IN SUDS?
WHAT'S THAT?

07:47.701 --> 07:49.571
- WELL...
[clears throat]

07:49.603 --> 07:51.543
FIRST THEY FLOOD THE DANCE FLOOR
AT BABYLON WITH SOAPSUDS.

07:51.572 --> 07:53.512
- AND THEN EVERYONE STRIPS
DOWN TO THEIR UNDIES...

07:53.541 --> 07:56.811
- OR LESS, AND DANCES...
CHEEK TO CHEEK.

07:56.844 --> 07:59.114
- SOUNDS AWESOME.
- IT'S DISGUSTING.

07:59.146 --> 08:00.106
- SEE YOU THERE?
- CAN'T WAIT.

08:00.147 --> 08:02.777
- MM.

08:02.816 --> 08:04.586
- YOU BETTER BE THERE TOO.

08:04.618 --> 08:06.688
- DON'T WORRY.

08:06.720 --> 08:09.020
- GUESS WHO'S
HEAD OVER HEELS?

08:09.056 --> 08:10.716
- I THINK YOU MEAN
"HEELS OVER HEAD."

08:10.758 --> 08:12.058
[laughter]

08:12.092 --> 08:13.532
- DOES MICHAEL HAVE
A BOYFRIEND?

08:13.561 --> 08:14.801
- THAT'S NONE
OF YOUR BUSINESS.

08:14.828 --> 08:16.728
- I JUST WANT TO KNOW.

08:16.764 --> 08:19.804
- WELL, DON'T STICK YOUR TIT IN
WHERE IT DOESN'T BELONG.

08:19.833 --> 08:20.803
- OW.

08:20.834 --> 08:26.774
[crickets chirping]

08:40.153 --> 08:43.123
[new age music]

