* NEVER THOUGHT
IT COULD GET WORSE *

09:50.791 --> 09:54.091
* TODAY, TODAY

09:54.127 --> 09:57.727
* TRAPPED INSIDE
A UNIVERSE *

09:57.765 --> 10:00.695
* ALL ALONE

10:00.734 --> 10:04.344
* ALONE IN THIS PARTY
